{"_path":"/quakes","_dir":"","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"雷神之锤","description":"每个人都有梦想，而游戏就是梦想的解药","navigation":false,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":"doom, book, translation"},{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"},{"name":"author","content":"tyyuan"}]},"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"back-to-top","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"chapter-header","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第十一章：雷神之锤"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"每个人都有未曾满足的梦想。\n有的梦想，比如开飞机、开赛车，可能太过昂贵或者需要太多的时间。\n有的梦想可能太过于天马行空，比如和外星人打仗、追猎吸血鬼。\n又或者，这些梦想本身就是违法的：比如在郊区里裸奔，或者用霰弹枪给自己的上司来上一梭子。\n但是无论如何，这些想法就在那里，每日每夜的萦绕在脑海之中。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"doing","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"prev-next","props":{},"children":[]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:14.quakes.md","_source":"content","_file":"14.quakes.md","_stem":"14.quakes","_extension":"md"}